度参与各个开发环节上还不具备太多的实践意义，但能给游戏产品「打辅助」，提供用户需求行为、竞品分析、玩法规则等方面的功能性建议。 因大幅提升了认知智能水平，将 AI 的理解和生成能力拔到新高度，ChatGPT 成为了「当红炸子鸡」。它会给游戏行业带来什么改变？ 记者就此话题「采访」了 ChatGPT，它表示自己可以为游戏行业带来一些独特的贡献，具体在四个方面：游戏对话、游戏内容生成、游戏测试、游戏辅助。最后，ChatGPT 不忘强调「这取决于游戏开发者如何使用我的技术。」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-76ebd837c18eaa91c096637fe7ad133b_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/582758454"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ij53ti4Tn/rVKEAMaCDkxNzgzMzM2IM6UjJ8GMAA4TEAacgk1ODI3NTg0NTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1675840108.027904", "card_id": "Q_582548111", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "不适合科研但非要读博会怎样？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "从各方面看都不适合科研，尤其是心态不好内耗严重 之前几段科研经历都让我十分痛苦 但就是对科研有种执念，对其它工作都不感兴趣 这种情况下我是应该放下执念还是撞个头破血流呢"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/582548111"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ij53ti4Tn/rVKEAMaCDkxNzM2Mzk3IOfchJ8GMAE4SkAbcgk1ODI1NDgxMTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1675840108.0284798", "card_id": "Q_581989604", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "感情里到底是「同频」重要还是「互补」重要？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-0cc26a098460a893b494aaac855838a5_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "